---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | HIIT Workout Timer | AI Fitcopilot"
  description="Privacy policy for HIIT Workout Timer and AI Fitcopilot. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data."
  canonicalUrl={new URL('/privacy', Astro.url.origin).href}
>
  <div
    class="relative min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden text-white selection:bg-orange-light selection:text-black"
  >
    <main class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24">
      <h1 class="mb-8 font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mb-8 text-sm text-white/60">Last updated: March 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-white/90">
        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">1. Overview</h2>
          <p>
            HIIT Workout Timer and AI Fitcopilot (&quot;we&quot;, &quot;our&quot;, or &quot;the
            app&quot;) respect your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use
            it, and your rights regarding your information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We collect information you provide and data generated when you use our services:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
            <li>
              <strong>Account information:</strong> When you sign up or log in (via email/password or
              Google/Apple Sign-In), we store your email address, display name (if provided), and authentication
              identifiers.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Workout and activity data:</strong> Workout logs, session duration, rounds, timers
              used, and progress data you create or sync.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Usage data:</strong> General analytics to improve the app (e.g., features used,
              errors).
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use the following third-party services to operate the app:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
            <li>
              <strong>Supabase:</strong> Authentication, database, and backend hosting. Their privacy
              policy applies to data stored with them.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Google Sign-In:</strong> When you use &quot;Continue with Google&quot;, Google may
              collect and process data per their
              <a
                href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
                class="text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 underline"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a
              >.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Apple Sign-In:</strong> When you use &quot;Continue with Apple&quot;, Apple may
              collect and process data per their
              <a
                href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/"
                class="text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 underline"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a
              >.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">4. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
            <li>To provide and personalize the workout timer, HUD, and activity tracking.</li>
            <li>To authenticate you and secure your account.</li>
            <li>To improve our services and fix bugs.</li>
            <li>To comply with legal obligations when required.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We use industry-standard measures to protect your data, including secure connections
            (HTTPS), authentication through trusted providers, and access controls. Sensitive data
            is stored with our database provider (Supabase) under their security practices.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>
            Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or export
            your data. You can request account deletion or data export by contacting us. You may
            also revoke access granted to third-party sign-in providers (e.g., Google or Apple)
            through their account settings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">7. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For privacy-related questions or requests, contact us at the support or contact channel
            provided in the app, or via the main website.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-12 text-sm text-white/50">
        <a href="/" class="text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300">Return to home</a>
      </p>
    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
